cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE 

This paper is about automatic generation of benchmarks for named entity recognition and entity linking, which are tasks related to natural language processing and information retrieval. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Other likely sub-categories include cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
